snippet.title: Overcooked! All You Can Eat - Announcement Trailer (Switch, PS4, Xbox One, Steam)
snippet.description:
** BREAKING NEWS ** Overcooked! All You Can Eat comes to Nintendo Switch, PS4, Xbox One and Steam on March 23rd! Learn more: https://bit.ly/OCAYCELegacy

Both original games + extra content
New kitchens + chefs
Online multiplayer for ALL kitchens
Cross-play coming soon

Wishlist on Steam: https://bit.ly/OCAYCESteam

Official website: https://www.team17.com/games/overcooked-all-you-can-eat/
Follow on Twitter: https://twitter.com/Overcookedgame
Join the Discord: https://discord.gg/Overcooked
Follow Team17 on Twitter: https://twitter.com/Team17
Like Team17 on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/Team17/


About Team17 Digital Ltd
Founded in 1990, Team17 Digital Limited is a leading international games label that hosts the Worms franchise, Blasphemous, The Escapists, Moving Out, Overcooked, Neon Abyss, Going Under, Yooka-Laylee and many more from developers around the world. 


Visit www.team17.com for more info.


#NintendoSwitch #PS4 #XboxOne
